WEBVTT

00:00:05.383 --> 00:00:22.050 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m so happy that you’re my friend,
Just like David and Jonathan.

00:00:22.050 --> 00:00:37.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’re always there.
Thank you for you.

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:46.283 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You love Jehovah;
I do too.

00:00:46.283 --> 00:00:56.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s why we’re best friends,
Stuck like glue.

00:00:56.150 --> 00:01:08.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’re always there.
Thank you for you.

00:01:08.416 --> 00:01:12.983 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We laugh and play,
Study and pray.

00:01:12.983 --> 00:01:17.583 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love to walk with Jehovah each day.

00:01:17.583 --> 00:01:28.183 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when we’re in Paradise,
It will always be this way.

00:01:28.183 --> 00:01:45.383 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we have brothers, sisters too
Who love Jehovah like we do.

00:01:45.383 --> 00:02:00.316 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’re always there.
Thank you for you.

00:02:00.316 --> 00:02:13.183 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And I’m always here.
Thank you for you.

